A full text of this report and of the rapporteur’s statement will be mailed before the close of
                                this week.For text of the Committee’s
                                    report, submitted to the Council May 20, see League of Nations,
                                        Official Journal, July 1932, p. 1355;
                                    for text of the rapporteur’s statement,
                                    see ibid., p. 1222. [Reber.]
